## Deployment Instructions
To complete the Vercel Web Analytics setup:

1. Enable Web Analytics on your Vercel dashboard:
   - Go to your project's dashboard
   - Click the "Analytics" tab
   - Click "Enable" to activate Web Analytics

2. Deploy the application to Vercel:
   ```bash
   vercel deploy
   ```

3. After deployment, Web Analytics will:
   - Start tracking page views and visitors automatically
   - Create new routes at `/_vercel/insights/*`
   - Display data in the Analytics tab of your Vercel dashboard

## Verification
You can verify the Analytics implementation is working by:
- Checking the browser's Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`
- Visiting your deployed application and confirming events appear in the Vercel dashboard Analytics tab after a few moments

